{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4421bf7db4","title":"周恩来关于《江西日报》问题的第一次电报指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b31e7cb11","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":7,"articleId":"4421bf7db4","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"通讯","id":"d5cbd05390","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a48d6313e0","type":"title","text":"周恩来关于《江西日报》问题的第一次电报指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4421bf7db4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cdbed355b9","type":"paragraph","text":"江西省军区党委转江西省大中学校红卫兵司令部：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4421bf7db4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d062f2e296","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二日十七时二十分中央文革小组给你们的指示是确实的，希望你们立即执行。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4421bf7db4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d3c0b34c0","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中央三月十六日关于报纸问题的几项规定，《江西日报》已实行军管，它不是哪一派革命群众的报纸，不能只反映哪一派的观点和意见。暂时可只刊登新华社电讯和《人民日报》、《解放军报》、《红旗》杂志的社论、文章等，以便使江西全省人民能够保证听到最高统帅毛主席和党中央的声音。你们进了《江西日报》的同志，望能立即退出，以利报纸立即出版。至于《江西日报》的报头问题，因这四个字是毛主席亲笔题写的，以不改为宜。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4421bf7db4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d783100e5f","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4421bf7db4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b3f5102cf","type":"paragraph","text":"1967年5月7日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4421bf7db4","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}